CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 22, 1957, pg. 5 reads: "Honor Worthy Grand Matron - Members of the Order of Eastern Star honored its Worthy Grand Matron, Mrs. Esther Greene with a testimonial banquet at Central Baptist Church, June 17. Left to right: Mrs. Ellen Poole, Johnstown; Herbert Townes, State Grand Master; Mrs. Esther Greene, Worthy Grand Matron of Omega Grand Chapter; Mrs. Rebecca Webb, New York City, and Mrs. Mary Smith, Associate Grand Worthy Matron. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of men and women, including guest of honor Ester Green wearing chain collar and light colored dress, seated between Herbert Townes and Rebecca Webb, and Ellen Poole, third from right, seated at banquet table in Central Baptist Church for testimonial dinner
